pannells autopsy by medical examiner lawrence j denson led to 
an incorrect conclusion concerning the possible actions of mr 
pannell at the time he was shot 
the mistake permeated and distorted the investigation and the 
grand jury presentation the medical examiner has admitted his 
error del tufo said 
the attorney refused to answer questions and left the news 
conference 
