barclay training center the main barracks in the capital and took 
scattered rebel troops by surprise witnesses said 
does soldiers advanced behind their sole remaining tank toward 
two strategic bridges leading from downtown monrovia north to 
bushrod island site of the capitals port and launching point of 
the rebel invasion of the city 
