raised in recent inquirer articles 
he declined to comment on the documents disclosed today by the 
newspaper 
cumberland farms has 1100 stores and more than 9000 employees 
in new england new jersey pennsylvania delaware and florida 
it was listed by forbes magazine last december as the nations 
35th largest privately held us company with an estimated 3 
billion in revenue 
