examined saddams handwriting several months ago did not know the 
identity of his subject 
the report gave no further details of the handwriting analysis 
israeli officials routinely refuse to comment on activities of the 
mossad 
the newspaper said the results of the handwriting analysis were 
shown to israeli leaders to help them assess the degree of 
severity and importance that should be attributed to saddams 
threats and declarations 
in april saddam threatened to respond with binary chemical 
weapons if israel staged a nuclear attack on an arab country 
