shelter 
kelso said he was sorry he didnt contribute a recipe 
blackened redfish comes to mind he said with a laugh 
i dont begrudge this kind of thing theres no reason we 
cant acknowledge each others humanity and a sense that we 
each experienced this in a way thats appropriate to acknowledge 
he said 
