fear is that it would make them a target of the same pummeling the 
gop plan is now taking 
i dont think its generally helpful foley said of 
immediately producing a democratic package 
the maneuvering of the negotiators has begun to wear thin on at 
least some rankandfile members of congress 
i have news for you summiteers both republican and 
democrat rep robin tallon dsc said on the house floor 
the rest of america thinks youre acting like a bunch of 
children 
