start airing later this month aug 11 here and from aug 13 to 16 
in other cities 
the ho chi minh trail was far more than a trail it was a 
network of trails dirt roads and river crossings mostly covered 
by jungle that stretched south for 200 to 300 miles into laos 
cambodia and south vietnam 
it was heavily bombed by us warplanes and periodically 
